<p>SuSE Linux surpasses the hardware limitations and provides
<b>operating system power</b> and <b>performance</b> for most of the computer
platforms used today world-wide.</p>

<p>Not just the x86 platform, but also <b>handhelds</b> and <b>PowerPCs</b>
can be home to SuSE Linux. SuSE Linux also has its place in the high-end arena
on <b>SPARC</b> and Itanium workstations, as well as powerful z-Series- and 
<b>S/390</b> machines.</p>
